        "text": "The trader and the social media influencer shall be jointly responsible for compliance with the obligations set out in this Regulation. A trader who enters into an agreement with an influencer for a commercial communication shall take reasonable and proportionate measures of due diligence to ensure that the social media influencer complies with the requirements of this Regulation, specifically regarding the proper disclosure of the commercial intent.",
